AmSouth Bancorp said it willissue about 3,166,000 shares of stock to acquire FirstTuskaloosa Corp.    Under a previously announced merger agreement, Amsouthoffered 66 dlrs a share in Amsouth stock for First Tuskaloosa.    The company said First Tuskaloosa shareholders will receive1.978825 shares of Amsouth stock for each First Tuskaloosashare held when the merger is effected April 17.    First Tuskaloosa has assets of more than 425 mln dlrs.Amsouth's assets are about six billion dlrs. Reuter&#3;